{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This session will help you take advantage of the Multi-Touch features available in iOS. You will learn practical information about Multi-Touch APIs, touch routing, gesture recognizers, as well as guidelines for interoperating with the system and other apps, and pointers for how to create complex real-world user interfaces which make great use of Multi-Touch."}],"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-118-making-the-most-of-multitouch-on-ios"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by reading the transcript and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-118-Making-the-Most-of-MultiTouch-on-iOS"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"WWDC11","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"role":"sampleCode","title":"Making the Most of Multi-Touch on iOS"},"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/118\/","type":"reference","overridingTitle":"Read Transcript","isActive":true}},"sections":[],"references":{"https://nonstrict.eu/wwdcindex/wwdc2011/118/":{"type":"download","checksum":null,"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/118\/","url":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/118\/"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNot